The '''University of Universal Thought''' was a small [[University/Legends|university]] on [[Karideph]] founded by a group of radical alien [[Scholar/Legends|scholars]] that at the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] were sustaining an extended and highly-abstract discourse with the [[Kari]] group mind through one of the most respected [[Hatch|Hatches]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]].<ref name="GG6-1">''[[Galaxy Guide 6: Tramp Freighters]]''</ref>

